title: Tokenizing Gotchis - Pool Gotchi/Ghost
body:
You can lock a gotchi in a contract, getting in exchange an amount of tokens depending on the rarity, based on a chart to be voted by this DAO.

You can use this system to exchange one of your gotchis for an other gotchi available inside the contract, or you can sell the tokens for Ghost in the Gotchi/Ghost pool, or you can provide liquidity to the pool, making some true FRENS
author: 0x9A4B0dA9E8e5c7135cd7188Bd2e84DAc513C594b
